data.description: This Refined Residence is overflowing with charm, from the Brazilian Cherry floors and stone fireplace to the vaulted ceilings in the living and family rooms. On the first level, you’ll find a dedicated dining room, family and living rooms, and an open kitchen with a large island and bar seating. The kitchen also opens to a sizeable backyard with a large pergola, shading the patio, which has plenty of space for a grill, dining set, and hot tub! The first level also includes the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet, tall windows letting in abundant natural light, and a 4-piece ensuite. The top floor contains two bedrooms, a bathroom with his and her sinks, and a loft that can be used as a home office or children’s playroom. In the finished basement, there's a bathroom, storage room, and open space that could be converted into a craft room, home gym, or at-home theater. The basement also has an additional bedroom with an adjacent bonus room that could be used as a walk-in closet, music studio, or reading room. There’s also a dedicated mud and laundry room off the 3-car garage. This Lakewood home is within walking distance of a brewery, two local barbecue eateries, and Bear Creek, which offers several beautiful walking and biking trails and fishing spots. Other nearby amenities include four golf courses, and the Daniel Schaefer Athletic Complex.
